Dialogs.Dialog: （I came too early... I wonder what should I do）
You're early? Is my watch running late?
I'm restless today, somehow ... Were you too, perhaps?
Well then, since were early let's go.
▲高嶺＊＊▲. Sorry to keep you waiting!
What happened? Why are you in panic?
Eh... I'm sorry. Yeah, I have to calm myself down.
...No. I was acting like a kid too. Let's take deep breaths, right?
（▲高嶺＊＊▲, I wonder if you're here... Ah, there you are!）
Geez. There was a person over... And I thought it looked similar to you.
Are you looking forward to it so much?
Fufu! It's okay, I forgive you▼ Shall we go?
I wonder it I came too early... I was in a good mood.
I was watching. Geez, you're a meanie.
（I can't help but laughing because I was looking forward to our date!）
▲高嶺＊＊▲. Sorry to keep you waiting! ...Huh? Is something wrong?
▲主人公＊▲. No, I just couldn't sleep yesterday. I'm fine.
You can tell me if you're having problems, alright?
I'm fine! I've been looking forward to this.
I was picked up... I'm kidding. It's a coincidence.
Really. It's perfect we don't have to wait for each other.
Hey, can you look to your 0 right?
To the right?... There's nothing special...
I am! It's bad catching me from behind.
No, I was right here... Geez, you're so messy.
Oh...Haha, I couldn't wait so I came on a hurry. I wonder of you didn't see me,▲高嶺＊＊▲...
▲主人公＊▲. I'm sorry, I kept you waiting.
It's okay. What that your acquaintance?
Yes, from the neighborhood ...I was so happy that I went to talk a little, and then I saw you.
Perhaps it was the same when I left my house? I don't think so...
Hey, we still have some time, so why don't we go have some tea?
Ah, that sounds nice. Where should we go?
I still have time... I wonder if we should go into a store somewhere.
▲主人公＊▲. Hey, I'm a little tired.
Oh, do you have time, would you like some tea?
... Hey. Do you remember Valentine's Day?
Yes. I expect high things after this.
Hey~, do you remember last Christmas?
Of course, it's hard to forget.
Hey. Do you remember my last birthday celebration?
Hey, do you remember your birthday last time?
Of course I would remember your face.
...Hey, we celebrated our anniversary last time, right?
Do you remember it from time to time?
You told me I was a meanie
I said I needed a punishment
The time to be the best
...It's okay, that's fine. But next time I want to make more fun memories.
Memories... We really have a lot, right?
I'm sure there will be more fun in the future.
Will the album hold them all?
You can even build a house with this album!
...Yeah... Let's make more precious memories, right? Together.
I love you... I was thinking that.
That you tell me that, makes me happy.
...I saw you face, and I like you even more.
I want to confirm my connection with you.
The memories in my heart... I wonder if they're still in your heart.
There are so many memories together, I get lost.
That's right... They only continue to increase.
I wonder what will happen in the future...
I love you so much, I'll then love you more... I wonder what's next.
Do I have a lot of your time?
It's because I also have your time, right?
Yes. Because Aika's time is yours... I'm kidding.
You were so cute that time...
Cute, huh... I mean, you're more cute. Right, ▲高嶺＊＊▲?
... You cannot be told cute by anyone but me.
That's not bad, right? I'm the only one...
There are many things I want to talk about. I don't have enough time...
Isn't it okay today? We can speak.
...Is that right? We'll be together forever...
Do you remember me like this?
Isn't it no good? It's our history together.
I'm glad to hear that... You care about me as much as I do.
... I like you too, okay? As we get more memories, I like you more.
Can we be together a little longer?
Or maybe we still have time left.
Because I'm still with you... I'm happy, really.
Yes, me too. Let's have more fun together, right?
Is it okay to be together for a while longer?
Fufu~. Are you looking forward to it after this?
Yes. Can we stay together longer?
...Hey~. I wonder if I'm getting too excited.
Do you think it's okay to be more active?
Really? I don't think I can accept your words.
It's a pity. I'm getting greedy today.
I see. I'll do my best to enjoy our time.
Are we still good on time?
Why don't we stop by the nearby park? I want to relax a little... I'm kidding.
Emm, Hey? I want to go back to the park... What do you think?
Yes, sounds nice. Let's take a break.
Hey, isn't there a park ahead?
It seems something good happens when you go closer.
Hey. Why don't we take a rest at a nearby park?
Yes, right now? Are you tired?
Yes, you know? Can we rest a little? There's a park over there.
Hey, why don't we stop at the park?
Park? it's okay, if you want.
...I want to go to the park!
Fufu! I made you say it. Shall we go?
Ha~a... Did you enjoy yourself today?
Yes. I don't have any days that aren't fun.
Have you never go on dates? Really?
It's true... Before I met you, I never had this much fun.
Thank you for today. Did you have fun?
Yes. We've been on a few dates lately, so it's been great.
Oh! No, I didn't mean that!
At least that's how important it is, right?
Hmm, a little bit. I haven't been sleeping lately...
Because you call me a lot, and we're together a lot.
Hmm... You haven't called me so much... I wonder if you were worried about it.
No.I know it's not a lot, it's not that I don't understand you value your time with me.
We moved a lot today. Are you okay?
Yes... Hey, can we hold hands?
...Because of it, I can feel your body temperature. Otherwise, I'm restless.
...Hey. Your hand... can we hold hands?
We don't have that many opportunities to interact with each other, right?
I was worried. Just a little bit. But I understand that you care about me, right?
▲高嶺＊＊▲. Can you come a little closer?
Ah~... That's no it! ...Recenlty, when we do that... we end kissing, right?
That's why I was thinking... What would I do if you dislike it...
I don't hate it, I'll never do!
...The distance between us... Are you nervous?
We haven't been kissing recently. Do you hold back?
I wondered why at first... But I think that's being kind too.
Dissatisfied? Of you,▲高嶺＊＊▲? No way!
Ah~, I'm sorry. If you did, I...
Um, you always say that my food is delicious.
Ah, that was it. It's always delicious, so I never lie!
It's good to have a relationship where you can say things clearly.
You always tell me about my cooking.
Ah... Sorry, you can say whatever you want.
I'm so happy, so it's okay. I'm getting motivated by it, okay?
Isn't it? You take a lot of time when taking my photo... so I wonder.
When you say that... Is that right?
Hey~, memories aren't the type to leave on tape... I wonder what you think.
How about... Emm, what do you mean?
You don't take a lot of photos, right? So, I wonder if that's the case.
I see... I wasn't thinking about that.
I'm glad... Don't be shy to take my photo.
Thank you for always being with me.
What are you saying so suddenly.
My clothes, my hair style, and so on. It's okay, you praise me a lot, don't you?
If you think it's to your taste... I'm so happy.
...I'm so happy to have someone to accept me.
Hmm... I been recently chosing things that don't suit your taste...
Ah, clothes... Is that a burden to you?
No, at any rate, I know you better... I'd be happy if you could say it clearly.
I see. But it's not something to apologize for... right?
Looking at the recent history of emails coming to my cell phone, I laughed at your name.
It's because... If you think about it, your favorite person thinks about you so much.
I've been doing it for a long time... right?
Yes. Don't keep your eyes down.
I've been reading the emails I received from you...
Are you writing so much that you read it back?
The emails you send me from time to time are important to me... like love letters.
When you go out with me, have a meal, have a cup of tea, etc...You give priority to what I like?
Of course. It's natural that I knew about girlfriends.
Ah~, again with the proud face. But it's true.
That's a bit forceful... But I don't hate it, though.
...Because you're like that, I... I want to be with you. Forever and ever.
Can I stay by your side? Closest to you.
...I want to be that person to you. I want to be next to you forever...
I love you. There's no more to say...
I like you because you're like this. I like you. I love you.
...Please let me stay next to you.
Even if you say no, I won't listen... I'm kidding.
Because you're like this, I... fell in love with you.
...Because you're like this, I don't want to leave. For a little while.
Please, don't let go? I want to stay with you forever...
... You know? I want to be with you forever.
Is it okay to be next to you...?
...Because you're like this, I'm obsessed with you.
Whether I'm sleep or awake... all I think is about you... It's unfair I'm the only one.
So... don't let me go. Never. Promise me.
...Don't you know unless I say it?
...Geez.... I love you. Let me stay by your side forever...?
I love you... I don't want to be away from you...
I may not say such a thing, but...
Please, hug me... Don't let me go, okay?
Because you're like this, I'm attracted to you.
Ever since I met you... I can't stop myself.
So, please... Let me stay by your side? Keep me close...
Don't leave me... I'm sorry, it's nothing... I love you.
What can I do, I love you more... If you're a good boy... I want you to invite me on a date like today.
I'm glad I was born... It's not an overstatement. That's how happy I am today and I love you too much.
...Why happy times have to end in a blink of an eye. More, more, more... I wish we could be together.
While I'm with you... I've been really, really happy. I want to date like this again... I'll be waiting...
I think you're the only one who makes me so happy. Will you keep me this happy forever?
I don't want to say it's over... Thank you, I had so much fun... I'm very happy.
Thank you so much for making me so happy today. I was so satisfied... I just want to sleep. Fufu, it's funny.
Ha~... Hey, can I say it? It was the best! I'm kidding. Fufu!
...I knew it would be annoying if I say something like this... But...
I still want to be with you.
I don't want to go home...
...I have to hold back today. Then, next time?
I want to yell at the mountains.
Geez.... I wish time could stop as it is... Bye bye.
...What I should do. Geez, I don't want to move...
Hey... Can we do it once more?
▲高嶺＊＊▲... you don't want to go home.
I wanted to do it your way... Bye bye.
Even if you said such thing...
...No, I have to go home. See ya.
Yes... But, even at evening it's beautiful.
Yes, certainly the cherry blossoms lit by the sunset...
It's warm and it feels good...
Hey, where do they lit up the cherry trees?
It's a big event, so you can expect great things.
At night, there's a food stall... Can we go?
I don't think there's such thing.
Haha, then we can wait for it.
...Hey~, do you think on the legends about cherry blossoms?
Hmm. Like something scary under the tree, or the like?
What did you say that? Now I'm thinking about painful images.
I fell in love with the petals due to my past, and tears flow when I remember my lover. Now, it's changed.
You are my sun. Just being there makes my heart feel warmer... You're the sun in my sky.
Looking at the cherry blossoms next to you... I can't feel sad.
▲主人公＊▲, Thank you for finding me.
Yes. Ah~, there is the southern sky.
Do you see the red fruit over there?
Ah, there it is. Can you eat it?.
It's medicine, so I think you can eat it if you want to. Want to try it?
Yes, I think that's better ... I really like the Southern sky.
The color of autumn leaves is beautiful... from orange to red.
He~e... Next time I'll take a look.
The year is almost over... So, next year?
Fufu, yes. Right this way, please▼
It's quite different when it's lit up, compared to the evening.
It's stunning... I prefer the sunset.
By the way▲高嶺＊＊▲, did you just look up something on your phone?
Ah~, I'm sorry. I was really curious...
If the southern fruits are edible.
Hahaha. And what did it say?
You can eat it, but it's bitter and sour, so I should not do it.
There are people who have eaten it...
Fufu~. Next time, right? The flower language of Nanten is written like...
He~e, it has a meaning too. What does it mean?
I was surprised. It seems that my feelings were guessed.
There's still a little time left until it starts.
Do you want to get ready by looking at the pamphlet while drinking tea somewhere?
Hmm. But the pamphlet does say something important?
But I guess they won't post it until the end.
Well, that's right. Okay, let's do it!
...Hey, huh, isn't it the punch line?
It's okay. It's not that, probably.
It didn't look like the director's first work. Anyway, he said it was tough.
Yes. I think making something from scratch to make a movie is hard.
Hey. If we were to make something together, what would you choose?
Together, you mean... making sweets? While▲高嶺＊＊▲ teaches me.
Fufu, yes. Then it's going to be really soon.
▲高嶺＊＊▲? Do you have something you want to make?
Me? Well, I like making sweets, the rest is cooking.
Then... Ah~, I want to make a chair and a table with cute designs.
But what I want to make the most is-- a future with you.
Yes. Don't let me go, okay? I want to create a world next to you.
...I'm kidding. I might be influenced by the last scene of the movie.
Well then, maybe I'll be affected too.
Let's go, ▲高嶺＊＊▲! Our adventure is just beginning!
I just told you! Let's go! Hold my hand!
It might be very fresh to have a bowling showdown with strangers.
Phew. As expected, the team over there is strong!
I'm very good at it and I feel like I'm used to throwing.
Right, but my hands hurt already...
I'm doing some small mistakes, so let's go carefully?
Emm. Can you hold my hand?
...Be careful not to hurt your hand anymore.
I'm sorry, I don't know if it will work.
You've made it, you've won the championship!
No, I'm happy, okay? But... I think the lovey dovey couple award better... I'm kidding.
But after taking with for a year, the kiss on the cheeks are a little...
Well, I still think it's okay!
Hmm... it's true. After that, and again... I will take it...
I forget about time when I'm in such places.
There are many shops here, so there's not enough time.
It wide, so it seems likely you'll get tired.
Certainly. But at that time, there was a delicious smell.
Agreed. I want to eat a crepe▼
By the way. Where are we going next?
Ah~, can we go to the bookstore?
It's fine. What are you looking for?
I'd like to see a book about sweets and one about cooking.
...I didn't say a word about to make something to you, did I?
Fufu~, geez. Look forward to it.
Ah~. Hey, Isn't it about time for the illumination to show up?
Hmm? Ah, it's true. Let's go!
Yes... it looks like I'm on the shores of the Milky Way.
▲高嶺＊＊▲ is Orihime and I'm Hikoboshi?
Which means that today is the only day we can meet once a year.
Fufu. I'll be glad if it's sunny.
Should we give up if it rains?
Hmm...No. If I am now, I will never give up.
I would have given up before I met you. But after...
I've been getting greedy about you. Therefore, I think I will never give up.
And you? Would you do your best?
Of course! I will do my best!
Hey, can you see this? It's a fight.
Ah, it's true. Oh, it's a continuation...
Her power just before that slap was amazing...
Grab that hand and kiss it at the end. Fufu, I'm relieved.
It's more like a feast than a relief.
They look happy on that last picture. They're both smiling.
This kind of presentation is also interesting.
That's right... Wow, isn't that a nice photo of a couple?
Hah~... The subtitle "The world's happiness to you"... Wasn't it a photo exhibition?
Seems the one who was watching was a loud mouth.
Fufu~, that's one way to say it. Like you mouth is broken, right?
Haha, I see. ▲高嶺＊＊▲, which one is the best?
Everything was good, but... what was the most memorable? A picture of a sea otter.
Ah, floating in the water while holding hands...
Huh, why is it holding them? I wonder if there's a reason.
...I don't think you need a reason to hold hands with your favorite person in the world.
We have some time left, so why don't we have some tea?
What do you want to do?
Hmmー... Ah~, maybe we should do that.
Emm... Ah~, I'm sorry! It looks delicious by the name...
▲高嶺＊＊▲, I wonder what will happen if I drink with you.
Mmm... Well, when I was little, I had a sip of Papa's beer...
Ah, it looks delicious just looking at the bubbles.
That's right, at that time, he was singing a song while spinning around.
If you do that, you'll get drunk quickly...
It looks like it was really hard, and he was in a good mood. So, isn't it right?
I'm looking forward to becoming an adult.
There are a lot of love songs.
Yes. They aren't all happy songs.
Hmm... Hey, do you often experience that kind of thing?
Did you get hints from real experiences and conversations with other people?
I see. So, can someone make our song?
Fufu~, I want to ask about it... I want to contine making stories together.
Do you think anyone want to sing it?
I wonder.... If possible, I just want it to be happy.
Fufu~. Ah~, it seems the second half is starting.
I wonder what I should chose. Sweets, drinks... food.
But... I worry about what to chose. Spaghetti, gratin, and katsudon all seem to be delicious.
Hmm? Scallop soy sauce butter rice ball?
Emm... I can't eat all that.
It's good for us both, eating little by little. We have time.
As you can see, it's gone.
... I wish I had studied a little more.
But your repertoire has increased a lot, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
My repertoire has increased, and I can sing it like this.
...Fufu~, I can't believe it. I was wondering if it was fun, so I don't know.
Yes, thank you. Keep showing me many different worlds.
I want to sing now. Just for you.
Yay! Wait a minute, I will try my best.
Is there any event on Couples Day?
Seems like the credits of that game that can be played by two people is unavailable.
Oops. Compatibility fortune- telling is also a target.
Okay, first of all, fortune- telling!
Sure. But, can I believe it?
Look at it. Isn't there an element that produces bad results?
No. I was exactly what you said. I got annoyed when I got very good results and when I was happy.
I'm sorry. Ah~, Hey~, do you want to play that game?
There seems to be a photo frame for Couples Day only.
We were able to take it well!
Alright, let's divide this in half...
......I wish I could take pictures of this kind every year.
No, not like that. Somehow, remembering this time, I want to chose a frame together like this――.
Before we notice it, we'll be both grandpa and grandma. That kind of thing is wonderful.
But by that time it seems to have faded.
...It's still good. What is important is that you are at the time.
Yes... that's right. Okay, we still have time, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Thank you. I'm gonna take another one with another frame.
Even though it's a mini live, there are quite a few people.
They broke the record of spectators at many live houses. That legendary song and making a debut with it!
...This band has a large fan base.
Nice explanation. As expected of,▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Oops, is it about to start?
I think so. Are you excited?
Even though it's summer, it looks like I'm seating.
Hey. maybe you'll want to drink water...
Ah~, let's go together. I want to breathe outside air.
You pushed me first, that's it!?
It was not intentional! You were hitting me hard during the live!
You have to do that in a live! That is the purpose!
This is bad... ▲高嶺＊＊▲, over here!
Ah... I was surprised... ▲高嶺＊＊▲, are you okay?
I was surprised... ▲高嶺＊＊▲. Don't you think it was crazy?
It's ridiculous. I'm glad those two guys calmed down.
......I thought you were getting involved... So I yelled...
...I see. Sorry to scare you. But thank you, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
No. I'm sorry. On the contrary, I was worried... Is it possible for me to protect you?
Some people are dancing, others are selling pictures ... I wonder why.
Hmm? Do you have any concerns?
Hmm... Hey, huh, how does that work?
You see that clown doll, it's bouncing...
Isn't it hanging with a thread or something?
Hey, can I see it from close?
What a reliable Watson-kun. Let's go!
（▲高嶺＊＊▲ is so curious and inquisitive!）
I think it's even more fun, even when ending.
I've always been thinking about it since I was a kid, and I'm waiting for loneliness after having fun.
Playing with friends or travel with your family. I'll be alone when I'm done. So, I was thinking that.
I forgot that, because you're right next to me.
Do you feel lonely after going back home?
... I'll be fine, because it's different from before.
Return home? Hey, I want to try that doll.
After practice, will you participate as a performer next?
（▲高嶺＊＊▲, I'm getting used to your cute smile...）
Can we go in the opposite direction today?
There's a building with the banner "Laser athletics".
Yes. I want to aim for a high score. Can we go for another lap?
Maybe there's an unknown attraction we haven't found yet?
I see. Let's go find another thing!
When I was a kid, I felt scared of the amusement park at night.
The electricity goes out, people are gone... Isn't it like a haunted house?
Yes. Now it's like a dream world.
Certainly. It's amazing because light make this place different.
Can you keep shining for me?
What if the battery runs out?
If that happens, I'll recharge it. Don't worry, okay?
...It's because it's the land of dreams.
Then I have to change my job. I wonder what I should do.
Do you want an immediate answer?
Haha~ Then I'll be exclusive to you, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
I think there are so many couples...
There's no clerk or staff here, are you tired?
But I feel happy after seeing them... that's what I think.
In short, it's best for us to have fun, and it seems that there are events unique to today.
Hmm~. Hey, what are the unique events of today?
No, what's that? Is there anything else?
This is the main event! "Honey Hug! Getting close and GO in a swimsuit!"
Because...really, there are only couples. Inside and outside. It's a landscape you can't easily experience.
Surely... Well, we are one of them.
...Somehow, there are some who are bold.
Yes. The one I saw was shy...
We would be embarrassed if we did that.
...... For me to focus only in you?
Otherwise, you'll want to run away...
Hey, I wonder what kind of movie it will be.
The one here is almost over, so maybe it's one that makes use of the screen?
Hmmー... Fufu~, no. I can't imagine it at all.
We haven't bought juice and popcorn.
Ah~. What do we do now?
I'm going to buy them. What would you like to drink?
Emm, I like the same thing as you.
Okay. I'm off, see you in a jiffy.
Just right. Here is your juice.
Did you loss? I was confident. It's a pity.
Phew, I still haven't figured you,▲高嶺＊＊▲...
Really. You can see well today. That's why it's cold...
Hey, that bright one is Venus?
Hey~, can you stretch your left hand towards the stars?
Just stretch your fingers... a little more... like that.
Fufu! A wonderful ring is completed▼
A ring made from a star... Is that right?
Ah...is it normal for a man's ring to have no stones on it?
Ah, maybe. Then this is not a ring.
Can you let me chose the ring that suits your finger?
Now then, let's go around for a walk.
Hey. Is there someone from were we can watch?
Seems like that... But you can't go in, as expected.
If we can enter... Have you always wanted to wait over there?
I want to see you in a good place,▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Don't you know where the fireflies will go?
Fufu! I'm happy just to spend the same time in the same place as you, right?
Well, I'm the same? Maybe I'm a bit greedy...
Yes. You though this for me, right?
... Thank you, I'm happy. I hope a lot of fireflies come by!
This is the first time I've seen fireflies...
Right. If you speak quietly, you can get near.
Fireflies shine even if they're male or female, but male shine brigthly, don't they?
To me, who gave off a weak light, you gave a strong light first, and at first I was confused... but happy.
Look there. A male is flying near a female.
That means, they are happy. Yes.
Hey. There are couple skating and ice dance, but what is the difference?
Hmmー? I feel like both are similar...
Geez. But, you can understand when you see them, right?
Don't you mind this synchronized skating?
Ah~, don't worry about it. No... I'm interested▼
Haha~, if you look forward to it, I will pass.
Oh, some players won the world championship! Together!
Is that so? What kind of person?
Not that, but... the scene from the previous show remains, I can't do it.
Well, the other person was a pro... So I think it'll be hard.
I should have done image training...
I knew it, you're amazing ▲高嶺＊＊▲...
But, I still can't do well.
Well, you were getting a lot of attention from the people around, so you were scouted.
Don't praise me like that... Meanie.
Phew... After all, it's fun to try new things.
That's right. Even by looking it was fun.
I got you to open the door again.
Not directly, but it's you after all. You're the only one that makes me want to challenge myself.
It will continue this way... Let's get along in the future, right?
This kind of place makes me very nervous...
You don't even want to participate?
I've been thinking about this for a while, and I may have said it. Be more confident.
It's no joke. ▲高嶺＊＊▲, you're so cute you can be included!
! Don't say it so loud... It's embarrassing.
......I'm sorry. I did it without noticing.
It's alright. I really enjoy it, but it's unfair to make you understand this way. Fufu.
"I want to try"... Did you think that?
It's fine. No one is watching!
Really? Should I practice more so that you can be fascinated like with that model?
... You know? I don't know why did I get angry when I said that...
When I look at your face... I was relieved you liked it... I love you more than I thought.
...So, right now, when I want to see your face, I don't have a limit, right?
Hey, I'm a little tired. Can we go?
Hey, is this ECO person famous?
Hmm. I wonder if it truly is famous.
Hmm... did you know about it?
A master of romance. What kind of woman is it?
I wonder if it's a woman.
Geez. Be more clear about it.
